devdoc.details: Implements a bidding auction with refund and claim mechanisms.

bid().details: Updates the winner - stores the bidExtend 10 minutes the auction if the new winner appears when the leftime is low than 10 minutes.

constructor.details: Initializes the auction contract and sets the owner and end time.

partialRefund().details: If the bidder is currently winning, only the non-winning part is withdrawable.

refund().details: The owner collects a fee from each bid. Losers are refunded their balance minus the fee.

returns._0: An array of structs with each bidder and their respective bid.
A struct containing the address and bid amount of the current winner.
